    "coordinatorGroup.edit.description.tooltip" => "Enter a description for your coordinator group. Associated job coordinators will be able to see this description.",
    "coordinatorGroup.edit.infobox" => "\nA coordinator group is an organizational unit in translate5 consisting of at least one job coordinator, to whom workflow steps can be assigned, and any editors created by the job coordinator, to whom the job coordinator can in turn assign their jobs.<br/>\nA coordinator group can be your external language service provider, for example, and the job coordinator is then your associated project manager.<br/>\nA coordinator group could also be a foreign branch of your organization that carries out reviews for you and coordinates them itself.<br/>\n<br/>\nCreate a new group here, then you can create the job coordinator belonging to the group in the user overview.\n                ",
